rating_comment: Very Clean rooms and bathrooms, Will get restaurent within walkable range. Safe and Best rooms to stay with family
Nice place to stay in Siliguri. Close to restaurants, friendly host, a clean room and good bed. Exactly what we needed for one night after a long journey.
OM Nivas was a nice place to stay and the host was very friendly and supportive.

Stayed for an overnight. Was welcomed with great hospitality. Uncle and Uncle are very courteous and is a great host. The rooms have all the basic amenities..
If you are looking for a value for money place to stay in Siliguri, this is a great place.

Property and owner is absolutely good. Mr. Saurav has arranged a rickshaw early in the morning which is very helpful but minor things was found missing. However I have trust because property is new but with experience it will be more efficient.
